cdata.name: IMMLA
cdata.desc:
IMMLA stands forInternational MultiModal Logistic Application and its a decentralizedmultimodal logistics service with a p2p system fortransportation, documentworkflowand payments.The mission of IMMLA project is a simple, clear and convenient interaction between the owner of cargo and the transporter on all stages of the freight transport.

Through the use of smart contracts, IMMLA is able to ensurepayment to the carrier regardless of its financial condition providing confidence and reliability.The terms of shipment, the current position of the cargo, its condition at the time of transfer of responsibility between carriers are recorded through the blockchain making the records 100% immutable.

IML are ERC20 Ethereum-based tokens and they represent ownership of the IMMLA platform. Tokens will also be used in the platform as a payment method. IMMLA alsoredeems & burns tokens at the expense of 36% of transportation revenue.
